===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|abime|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|abisme|lang=fro}} from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{term|*abyssimus|lang=la}}, a superlative of {{term|abyssus||bottomless pit|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἄβυσσος|lang=grc}}. Cognate to {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|abîme|lang=fr}}. See also {{m|en|abyss}}.<ref name=OCD>{{R:OCD2|page=6}}</ref><ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=11}}</ref>

